{"tid":2404893,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人地都道歉了 而且誠懇地也願意退款 這不是該給機會同路人嗎？","createTime":"2021-02-12T04:09:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T04:15:14.000Z","uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"83f40c3e8013555df4788e3d278b85d55e284b50","tid":2404893,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"其實大家點嬲都好 但係咪一定要講說話咁難聽同找渣的方式說話？ 文字沒有標點都罵一餐 這行徑如同5毛。。。有時做既欠缺經驗 所以出了大問題 大家都唔樂見 人地都道歉了 而且誠懇地也願意退款 這不是該給機會同路人嗎？ 如果大家連這樣的機會都不給予 同路人就會越來越少 走不下去了。。。雖然做什麼都難以補救 但至少係咪應該點嬲既話可以尊重返自己係有質素既香港人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74e30ec94c210c4131c1088eeb5346657d7032b","tid":2404893,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T04:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}